name: La Quietud Tiyoweh
review:
Very yummy overall! We ordered the special, and a pitcher of lemonade. We could see the waitress hand squeeze the lemons, with mint and water, and so it was.... Terrific service, waitress spoke great English and was willing to offer suggestions.  Location was excellent with inside and street seating.
Food was.... Delicious!! I highly recommend.  Such a delightful space. And, the people were lovely!.
